{"tid":1073493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU拍Netflix 劇照靚到黐咗線 連登仔係咪要暴動？","createTime":"2019-03-22T17:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T22:52:31.000Z","uid":152123,"like":22,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5125829cf69734651b516bb4b0dd5e95d81887","tid":1073493,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4pdJxg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4pdJxg.jpg&h=c7a93cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04810441c30955235cdb86615aa09b0b11ae6e4","tid":1073493,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"以青春愛情劇《夢想起飛》開啟演員生涯的「國民妹妹」IU，不僅以其清新脫俗的嗓音稱霸韓國歌團，只要出新曲皆能輕易攻佔排行榜，她精湛不造作的演技，更替她的演員身份穩固扎根，接連接演《王牌大明星》、《月之戀人－步步驚心：麗》等火紅影集的女主角&mdash;&mdash;如今，IU也晉升大銀幕，與Netflix合作推出電影長片《女孩，四繹》。<br />\n<br />\n《女孩，四繹》由四則不相干的故事組成，並且分別由四位韓國知名導演李京美、林弼成、全高雲、金宗寬拍攝。首部曲〈Love Set〉講述一個女孩與父親新歡（作為女兒的不能忍！）以網球對決來爭奪自己所愛。第二則故事〈Collector〉近距離描寫一對戀人間不安分的詭譎氛圍。第三段〈Kiss Burn〉找來影壇新星沈達琪與IU對戲，卻絲毫不見他有些許青澀。最後一則〈走在夜裡〉由IU與鄭俊元兩人主演，以一對男女在韓國古城街道漫步的緩慢步驟，娓娓回憶起兩人的過往回憶。<br />\n<br />\n除了主演四部曲的IU之外，國際知名女星裴斗娜，以及韓國實力派男星朴海秀等人皆前來助陣，各自激發出國民妹妹的不同面向。《女孩，四繹》將於4月5日於Netflix上架，喜歡IU的你，千萬不要錯過！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/persona-101-01-1553079646.jpg?resize=980:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2Fpersona-101-01-1553079646.jpg%3Fresize%3D980%3A%2A&h=4aa92995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ITH6ttdXBqk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DITH6ttdXBqk&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD152AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=ef58b5c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ITH6ttdXBqk</a>"},{"pid":"f5b12b1e1126b70239755a4f114f1dce0978ec32","tid":1073493,"uid":152123,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IU大叫：FxxK You！！！</span>"},{"pid":"241e1b0db8cccd90519424d31927e140e03bb345","tid":1073493,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/860d69e5f2fb548bc9ecd6a68050acca/5D166FEE/t51.2885-15/e35/53673364_1983964321731235_4226938847880315930_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F860d69e5f2fb548bc9ecd6a68050acca%2F5D166FEE%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F53673364_1983964321731235_4226938847880315930_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-arn2-1.cdninstagram.com&h=89a126ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8cf860d462331c69d66793274506d1fc5d7d276","tid":1073493,"uid":167658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tg3aLPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftg3aLPY.png&h=e630bf27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72f7ea297ee1ccea9bf35197a05d045420109a49","tid":1073493,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"食蘋果食到個樣咁臭都第一次見"},{"pid":"65da05ad8bdbdb1a24fb3a34e32a804cc1107a1b","tid":1073493,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"72f7ea297ee1ccea9bf35197a05d045420109a49","tid":1073493,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"食蘋果食到個樣咁臭都第一次見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T17:2